data.description: This is a stunning and spacious home that has undergone several recent updates, making it an excellent option for anyone looking for a move-in ready property. Updates completed in 2022 & 2023, including the kitchen, primary bath, and HVAC system. The HVAC system comes with a 10-year warranty, providing peace of mind for the new owners. The fireplace was also updated with marble tile, adding to the home's stylish aesthetic. Features 5-inch crown molding, marble tile flooring, and decorative lighting. There is also a study or office downstairs that provides privacy and space for those working from home. Additionally, the back section of the privacy fence was replaced 2.5 years ago, ensuring the property's privacy and security. Located in a desirable area with no neighbors behind you, this property is must-see. Don't miss your chance to view this beautiful home!
